{"tid":389114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"便便沖不走扔窗外誤墜玻璃縫 英女探頭撿糞被困 男友求助消防","createTime":"2017-09-06T03:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T03:50:04.000Z","uid":53379,"like":312,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8edd9942d42c831b137ec69b660b3d2ff4cf2060","tid":389114,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">便便沖不走扔窗外誤墜玻璃縫 英女探頭撿糞被困 男友求助消防</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170906/s00005/5228af8bc28671203b04a85c9ecd113b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170906%2Fs00005%2F5228af8bc28671203b04a85c9ecd113b.jpg&h=251952da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n窗口的兩層防盜設計使得紙巾被困在兩道窗戶之間。（史密夫GoFundMe眾籌頁）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170906/s00005/50193b0cb2e98680f6bbc876e7914c97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170906%2Fs00005%2F50193b0cb2e98680f6bbc876e7914c97.jpg&h=b5844800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子雙腳朝天卡在窗戶中動彈不得。（史密夫GoFundMe眾籌頁）<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170906/s00005/50193c4fd82af4c16a62edd9292a3080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170906%2Fs00005%2F50193c4fd82af4c16a62edd9292a3080.jpg&h=a2357f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後要呼叫消防部門把窗戶撬開以將女子拯救出來。（史密夫GoFundMe眾籌頁）<br />\n<br />\n第一次約會通常讓人心跳加速，然而英國布里斯托有一名女子在約會時發生意外，雙腳朝天地卡在窗戶，而當中原因更讓人哭笑不得。<br />\n<br />\n據悉這名女子是業餘體操運動員，經Tinder與對象大學生史密夫（Liam Smyth）在餐廳約會。情到濃時，兩人在餐後回到史密夫家中有進一步發展。然而女子在他的家中大便時，因廁所損壞不能沖水，於是試圖把糞便用紙巾包住扔出窗外庭院，然而窗口的兩層防盜設計使得紙巾被困在兩道窗戶之間，隨後女子把事件告知史密夫。<br />\n<br />\n由於這家房子是租住，因此史密夫認為需要把窗戶間的紙巾清理乾净。但棘手的是窗口的防盜設計令內部窗戶僅能開啟一道窄縫。無計可施之下這名女子竟然稱自己可以利用體操運動技巧，試圖穿越這條窄縫，最後導致女子雙腳朝天卡在窗戶中動彈不得。<br />\n<br />\n史密夫隨後試圖把女子拉出來但不成功。最後要呼叫消防部門把窗戶撬開以將女子拯救出來。事後史密夫把事件在眾籌網站GoFundMe分享故事，希望網民能資助他修理窗戶的金錢。截至目前，史密夫已籌得&pound;1,273英鎊（折合約$12,913港幣），遠遠超出籌款目標&pound;200英鎊（折合約$2028港幣）。<br />\n<br />\n史密夫表示對網民的支持十分感激，並計劃將多出的金錢捐給兩個慈善組織，分別是援助當地消防的慈善組織，以及協助貧窮世界國家人們有乾净衛生沖水設施的慈善組織Toilet Twinning。<br />\n<br />\n（英國廣播公司/GoFundMe）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170906/s00005/1504661675258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170906%2Fs00005%2F1504661675258&d=E2yCoEQOH8xopYD9uxQ%2Fpv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=cbd59228\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170906%2Fs00005%2F1504661675258&h=33a07f34\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170906/s00005/1504661675258</a>"},{"pid":"ee192c66f68da80005482bed8acfc21919fd2149","tid":389114,"uid":29781,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"本來都係少少柒 搞一大輪嘢之後仲柒"},{"pid":"a54958b892e7fecd365e087a4abaccb65c2cfd94","tid":389114,"uid":82532,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"以後點做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658db5728535b1cb99673d6775058d3a22d266a1","tid":389114,"uid":104081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4cbb84a8d09fadab62fbf28f865515b476dd470","tid":389114,"uid":108133,"like":95,"dislike":0,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:28:09.000Z","msg":"約會時柒一下已經慘<br />\n呢條女仲要柒幾鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d128e71450d1a07c5e1bb619eef65650dfe8df","tid":389114,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266d16861612c